The breakfast room was small, and the choice at breakfast was limited, but otherwise, this hotel was perfect.	Breakfast is adequate - fruit, cereal, bread, ham/cheese, basic cake/pastries.	The service at breakfast was prompt and the food was good.	The hotel itself is lovely and well-maintained with comfortable rooms; breakfast was the standard European variety and well done.	Breakfast at the hotel is adequate, although hot food is at an additional charge, so pastries, cereals etc available.	Service was great, especially the coffee & milk jugs at breakfast!